### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Marquer un message comme lu (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/mark-as-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_id": "message-uuid-here"
}

### Test 2 - Marquer plusieurs messages comme lus
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/mark-as-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_ids": ["message-uuid-1", "message-uuid-2", "message-uuid-3"]
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: message_id et message_ids manquants
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/mark-as-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 4 - Erreur: message_ids invalide
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/mark-as-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_ids": "not-an-array"
}

